Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:44.26,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad3\yshad6}鱼儿与太阳沉落于眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:48.51,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad3\yshad6}让我浸浴在它们的怀抱中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:58.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad3\yshad6}施下魔法 让绚丽的未知不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:03.32,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad3\yshad6}透过显微镜望去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:08.58,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad3\yshad6}那是一片碎裂的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:15.29,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad3\yshad6}我们是那曲旋律
